func Polynom-Evaluation (n,L,x) -> (Function of ( Polynom-Ring (n,L) ),L)
means
:Def5: (for p being (Polynomial of n,L) holds ( it . p ) = ( eval (p,x) ));
existence
proof
defpred P[ set,set ]
 means
(ex p9 being (Polynomial of n,L) st (p9 = $1 & $2 = ( eval (p9,x) )));
A1:now
let p being set;
