uniqueness
proof
let f being (Function of ( Polynom-Ring (n,L) ),L),g being (Function of ( Polynom-Ring (n,L) ),L);
assume that
A3: (for p being (Polynomial of n,L) holds ( f . p ) = ( eval (p,x) ))
and
A4: (for p being (Polynomial of n,L) holds ( g . p ) = ( eval (p,x) ));
